      <h2>How to Choose Based on Your Trade</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Framers & Rough Carpenters:</strong> Go with the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B076C3TB8P?tag=sciencesolved-20">BOSCH GLM165-40</a>. You need range and durability, and the Blaze Pro delivers both.</li>
        <li><strong>Finish Carpenters & Cabinet Installers:</strong> The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0FCM48QCM?tag=sciencesolved-20">Kiprim Green Laser</a> gives you the precision you need for tight tolerances.</li>
        <li><strong>Electricians & Plumbers:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C76CPGC7?tag=sciencesolved-20">BOSCH GLM100-23</a> is plenty of range and the small size fits in a pouch alongside your other tools.</li>
        <li><strong>Roofers & Siding Contractors:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DF7PB4QP?tag=sciencesolved-20">Tadeto Dual Laser 393FT</a> for the long range and daylight visibility.</li>
        <li><strong>Estimators & Project Managers:</strong> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B015FCJTEA?tag=sciencesolved-20">BOSCH GLM 50 C</a> for Bluetooth data logging and reporting.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Durability & Warranty Comparison</h2>
      <p>BOSCH offers the strongest warranty coverage in the category — their GLM series tools are backed by a 1-year warranty and a reputation for surviving hard job site use. The Kiprim and Tadeto units offer solid build quality with USB-C charging ports that are more durable than micro-USB. The Fanttik A11 Ultra has the most modern construction but the touchscreen is a potential failure point on dusty job sites.</p>

      <h2>Final Thoughts</h2>
      <p>You don't need to spend $200+ to get a great laser measure. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B076C3TB8P?tag=sciencesolved-20">BOSCH GLM165-40</a> at its current price point is the best balance of range, accuracy, and durability for the widest range of trades. If you're only working indoors, the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C76CPGC7?tag=sciencesolved-20">GLM100-23</a> saves you money without sacrificing quality.</p>
      <p><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B076C3TB8P?tag=sciencesolved-20" style="color:#3b82f6"><strong>Check current prices on Amazon →</strong></a></p>

